    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Spin a field of dark energy originating from you in a 4m radius sphere. The field moves with you and reduces your walking speed by half.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Each creature within the sphere must make a Constitution saving throw. A creature takes 12d6 necrotic damage on a failed save or half as much damage on a successful one. A creature must also make the saving throw when it enters the field's space for the first time on a turn or ends its turn there.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Any creature within the sphere is primed (necrotic). This condition ends immediately if the creature leaves the sphere.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>At Higher Levels: When you cast this spell using a spell slot of 5th level, increase the radius by 4m.</p>",
